                <tr>
                <th scope=\"row\">SCW35NE<\/th>
                <td>Test produced a collapse (whumpf) on a 35&deg; northeast-facing slope.<\/td>
                <\/tr>
                <tr>
                <th scope=\"row\">SCL40S<\/th>
                <td> Test produced a sluff on a 40&deg; south-facing slope.<\/td>
                <\/tr>
                <tr>
                <th scope=\"row\">SCN30N<\/th>
                <td>Test produced no result on a 30&deg; north-facing slope.<\/td>
                <\/tr>
                <tr>
                  <th scope=\"row\">SCS45NWR3D2<\/th>
                  <td>Test produced a slab avalanche on a 45&deg; northwest-facing slope. <br>
                  The avalanche was medium size for the path but large enough to injure or kill a person.<\/td>
                <\/tr>
              <\/tbody>
              <\/table>
